  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to increase the radiation dose (Boost) to the bladder tumor. The
      bladder cancer patients included in the study will undergo tumor demarcation. The bladder
      demarcations will then be the target for an image-guided boost delivered precisely to the
      expected tumor site.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
