  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Muscle invasive bladder cancer (transitional carcinoma)

          -  Unifocal

          -  TNM stage T2a-4a, N0-1, M0

          -  unfit for radical cystectomy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hyperthyroidism

          -  Multinodular goiter

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Breast feeding

          -  WHO preformance status more than 2

          -  Iodine allergy

          -  MRI or CT contrast media allergy

          -  Bi-lateral hip-prosthesis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
